attributes.title: WWE 2K17 Gameplay
attributes.caption: "That's the power of Japan!"
attributes.description: I hope you have enough creamer cups crammed in your pockets to last through a full hour of sweaty man-on-man action.

attributes.title: Emily Wants to Play Gameplay
attributes.caption: Bwaaaah bwuuuuuuuh... bwurrrrrrrrrrr...
attributes.description: It's almost an hour of pizza-delivery-turned-spooksville, so you may need to microwave your slice.

attributes.title: Worst Games of 2016 Gameplay
attributes.caption: Looks like you'll never be a bus driver, Adam.
attributes.description: Worf borf, I hope you don't expect Adam to be able change professions to something in the industrial sector. Here's an hour of him trying anyways, borf borf.

attributes.title: Resident Evil 7 VR Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Is he dead, or what?"
attributes.description: Not every Spooky McSpookerton can make it into the final product, so enjoy this 90-minute romp through downtown Spooksville and maybe even West Spooksville.

attributes.title: Axis Football Gameplay
attributes.caption: "The New England Volunteers??"
attributes.description: I was thinking of the description for this video while having a super bowel movement. Anyway, enjoy your uncut football good-times.

attributes.title: SEUM: Speedrunners from Hell Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Craig's top ten sad days since Nintendo Power ended..."
attributes.description: I brought you a treat. It's 45 minutes of Craig lamenting the death of Nintendo Power on December 11th, 2012.

attributes.title: Alekhine's Gun Gameplay
attributes.caption: "I'M JUST THE BELLHOP, SIR."
attributes.description: How many of history's big baddies can Alekhine take out in 45 minutes? Answer: One... maybe one....

attributes.title: Sniper Elite 4 Gameplay
attributes.caption: "That's just one! He can still have kids!"
attributes.description: Balls, balls, balls, a whole hour of balls!

attributes.title: Back in 1995 Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Which of you guys have put your penis in a vacuum?"
attributes.description: Pull your peener out of that bag of banana peels and point your peepers hither for a while, m'lady.

attributes.title: Fast RMX & Bomberman R Gameplay
attributes.caption: "You're stuck. You're die."
attributes.description: I'm gonna be honest, "and 10 minutes of Switch setup" made the title a bit too long, so I'm just letting you know right here.

attributes.title: Mass Effect Andromeda Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Do you think you'll have sex with your dad before he dies?"
attributes.description: Trust me when I say that watching an unedited hour of Mass Effect: Andromeda gameplay feels like a 600 year journey in to another galaxy.

attributes.title: Guts and Glory Gameplay
attributes.caption: "It said Mr. Yang's favorite movie was Fast and the Furious!"
attributes.description: You'll be delighted to hear that you get to spend this uncut video exploring the beautiful mind of Jon Smith. Will you emerge unscathed?

attributes.title: My Summer Car Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Now it's just making a grinding noise..."
attributes.description: Good news, FIRST member! Due to the nature of this game, the video feels 100x longer than it actually is!

attributes.title: Real Heroes: Firefighter Gameplay
attributes.description: While you watch this hour-long video, it's possible that 90% of married firefighters around the world have committed at least 19 adulterous deeds each.

attributes.title: Outlast 2 Gameplay
attributes.caption: "JAMES. Do you have... the belt?"
attributes.description: Can poor Jacob evade angry hillbillies and Scientologists for an entire hour while also pretending to be Bruce as he berates Jacob while he impersonates... oh jeez, my head...

attributes.title: Secret Service Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Take him down, dear!"
attributes.description: Is an hour long enough for a jacked secret service agent to save our country? Probably not...

attributes.title: Prey Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Might as well uninstall the game..."
attributes.description: If the unedited friendship between Steven and Lawrence can survive this video, anything is possible.

attributes.title: WWE 2K17 Gameplay: WWF Pay Per View
attributes.caption: "Those are world-ending legs you've got there, Matt."
attributes.description: Here's 90 minutes of pure adrenaline pumping through Sacramento's collective veins. Eat your heart out, WWE.
attributes.display_title: WWE 2K17 Gameplay: WWF Pay Per View

attributes.title: Drunk E3 2017 - EA Press Conference
attributes.caption: "You ever masturbate and then have sex and it just takes forever?"
attributes.description: If you stick around long enough, you can watch 4 different groups of drunk people have separate conversations at the same time.

attributes.title: Drunk Battlesloths Gameplay
attributes.caption: "It's weird how the Battlesloths theme is the same as iZombie..."
attributes.description: Sure, there's 15 minutes of setup, but watching a conveyor belt of drunk goofballs cycle into the webcam warrants a little wiggle room.

attributes.title: Drunk E3 2017 - Bethesda/Devolver Digital Press Conference
attributes.caption: "So much.. character."
attributes.description: It's like Skyrim with VR! It's like Fallout with VR! It's like Bethesda with VR!
attributes.display_title: Drunk E3 2017 - Bethesda/Devolver Digital Press Conference

attributes.title: Drunk E3 2017 - PC Gaming Press Conference
attributes.description: Prepare to be graced by the dynamic duo of drinking before noon, Lawrence and Omar! There's an hour of PC stuff as well.
attributes.display_title: Drunk E3 2017 - PC Gaming Press Conference

attributes.title: Drunk E3 2017 - Playstation Press Conference
attributes.caption: "Destiny's just Warhammer. Why did I say that out loud?"
attributes.description: It's like Skyrim with VR! Wait... I already did that in another Drunk E3 description. Destiny looks cool though.

attributes.title: Drunk E3 2017 - Xbox Press Conference
attributes.caption: *GASP* Ori...
attributes.description: With the nonstop barrage of rad indie titles, Porsches, and Gareth Coker on a piano, behold what inebriation can do in the face of a pretty good E3 press conference.

attributes.title: Dragon Ball Xenoverse Gameplay
attributes.caption: "That's good. Sexy, but dangerous."
attributes.description: Here's a real treat for you FIRST members. After the Xbox Conference, James had himself a little jaunt through Dragonballsland, and you will be the sole witnesses of his adventures!

attributes.title: Sayaka Gameplay
attributes.caption: "I'm just good. I'm just guh, g-guh, good at it!"
attributes.description: Watch a gamer go head-to-head with his broken game for a very unbroken hour.

attributes.title: Ultimate Epic Battle Simulator Gameplay
attributes.caption: "History is amazing. There, I said it."
attributes.description: Fun fact: The length of this unedited gameplay is less than 10% the run time of the entire Lord of the Rings trilogy (extended editions, of course).

attributes.title: System Hack Gameplay
attributes.caption: "The hacker eventually becomes the hackee."
attributes.description: This one's basically an hour-long documentary about a strange creature in its natural habitat.

attributes.title: Weed Shop 2 Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Can you pawn these too? They're Adam's glasses."
attributes.description: This uncut chapter of the Tug Nuggets saga is, as the kids say, quite dank.

attributes.title: Perception Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Don't be bored by blindness. It's the most exciting thing in the world!"
attributes.description: Oh hey, how'd we get here again? Here's an uninterrupted hour of us making fun of blind people.

attributes.title: Clone Drone in the Danger Zone Gameplay
attributes.caption: "There you go. Like Mace Windur!"
attributes.description: Sure, the Geonosis arena battle isn't nearly as long as this uncut gameplay, but it still feels like an eternity of suffering and terrible droid puns.
attributes.display_title: Clone Drone in the Danger Zone Gameplay

attributes.title: James Cameron's Avatar Gameplay
attributes.caption: "I 100% saw Avatar four or five times, and that's not in the movie."
attributes.description: Elyse had to spend an entire hour covered in dots in a green screen studio in order to bring you this uncut video.

attributes.title: Call of Duty: WWII Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Do you know how long COD has been a video game? 45 YEARS."
attributes.description: Careful, watching this much unedited COD can have some pretty dank side effects.

attributes.title: The Tearoom Gameplay
attributes.caption: "He didn't wash his hands. Disgusting."
attributes.description: Here's another throbbing, veiny full gameplay for you fine folks.

attributes.title: Beast Battle Simulator Gameplay
attributes.caption: "IT'S A SUICIDE PTERODACTYL!"
attributes.description: Eyyy bucko, you want some animals on a Monday? I've got a whole hour of creepy critters for your weekly cravings. Take 'em and cake 'em if you know what I'm sayin', eyyyyy.

attributes.title: Marc Ecko's Getting Up: Contents Under Pressure Gameplay
attributes.caption: "IT'S A PURSE. FOR. CANS."
attributes.description: Okay kiddies, take a break from your bi-daily teepeeing rampages and watch an hour of REAL art.
attributes.display_title: Marc Ecko's Getting Up: Contents Under Pressure Gameplay

attributes.title: Everybody's Golf Gameplay
attributes.caption: "I'm the true mathlete!"
attributes.description: This ain't your average golf-related Fullhaus, FIRST folks! This week it's 18 unedited holes of Joel.

attributes.title: Drunk Cuphead Gameplay
attributes.caption: "Anyone want a milk shot?"
attributes.description: I've got a Fullhaus 'sclusive for you folks. Let the drunken Cupheading commence!

attributes.title: Drunk SNES Classic Gameplay
attributes.caption: I LOOOOVE L.A.
attributes.description: The 2-hour descent into madness has arrived, and Randy Newman is here to hold your hand.

attributes.title: Surfers VS Skaters Gameplay
attributes.caption: "These guys are a bunch of groms."
attributes.description: This is less of a full gameplay and more of a 40-minute improv sesh.

attributes.title: Avatar 2 Gameplay
attributes.caption: "I'm always in slow motion."
attributes.description: Neytiri's back with some uncut bits for James Cameron's viewing pleasure.

attributes.title: Evil Possession Gameplay
attributes.caption: "I never went camping."
attributes.description: Technically there's a s'more game in there too, but it's merely an appetizer for some unedited campfire spookums!
